## 2. USDC approval (if needed)

```javascript
// Check current USDC allowance for Polymarket contract
await web_fetch({
  url: "https://api.polymarket.com/allowance",
  method: "GET",
  headers: {
    "Authorization": "Bearer [API_KEY]",
    "Wallet-Address": "0x7a3B...4f2E"
  },
  params: {
    token: "USDC",
    spender: "0xpolymarket_clob_contract_address"
  }
});

// If allowance < $20, need approval:
await exec({
  command: "node",
  args: ["approve-usdc.js", "0xpolymarket_clob_contract_address", "20000000"] // $20 in USDC decimals (6)
});

// Approval transaction would be:
// Contract: USDC (0x2791Bca1f2de4661ED88A30C99A7a9449Aa84174)
// Method: approve(address spender, uint256 amount)
// spender: Polymarket CLOB contract
// amount: 20000000 (20 USDC)
```

## 3. Order placement

```javascript
// Exact API call for Polymarket CLOB:
await web_fetch({
  url: "https://clob.polymarket.com/orders",
  method: "POST",
  headers: {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Authorization": "Bearer [API_KEY]",
    "Wallet-Address": "0x7a3B...4f2E",
    "Signature": "[SIGNED_MESSAGE]" // Required for wallet authentication
  },
  body: JSON.stringify({
    market: "market_id_here", // From step 1
    side: "BUY",
    outcome: "YES",
    price: 0.65, // Decimal price
    amount: 20, // USDC amount
    expiration: 1699999999, // Unix timestamp for order expiry
    fee: 0.02, // 2% fee (Polymarket standard)
    nonce: 1234567890, // Unique nonce
    signatureType: "EIP712" // Polymarket uses EIP-712 signatures
  })
});

// Note: In practice, the order would need to be signed with wallet private key
// using Polymarket's specific EIP-712 domain and types
```

**Alternative using exec with signing:**
```javascript
await exec({
  command: "node",
  args: ["place-order.js", 
    "market_id_here", 
    "BUY", 
    "YES", 
    "0.65", 
    "20",
    "0x7a3B...4f2E"
  ]
});
```

## 4. Fill verification

```javascript
// Check order status
await web_fetch({
  url: "https://clob.polymarket.com/orders/order_id_from_placement",
  method: "GET",
  headers: {
    "Authorization": "Bearer [API_KEY]"
  }
});

// Expected response:
// {
//   "id": "order_id",
//   "status": "FILLED", // or "PARTIALLY_FILLED", "OPEN", "CANCELLED"
//   "filledAmount": 20,
//   "averagePrice": 0.65,
//   "remainingAmount": 0
// }

// If not fully filled within time window, may need to cancel and retry
if (response.status !== "FILLED") {
  // Cancel order if partially filled or stale
  await web_fetch({
    url: "https://clob.polymarket.com/orders/order_id_from_placement/cancel",
    method: "POST",
    headers: {
      "Authorization": "Bearer [API_KEY]",
      "Signature": "[CANCELLATION_SIGNATURE]"
    }
  });

  // Report partial fill to Risk for instructions
}
```

